data.description: An extremely commuter-friendly home close to retail, dining, and services. This bi-level gem offers so much, so, let’s take a look!!  Having a thoughtfully designed layout, the lower level presents a private retreat which boasts a spacious family room perfect for gatherings, a large room for a home office, guest area, a workout room, sewing room etc. It also includes a full bathroom, complete with a laundry area, providing the utmost convenience. The entire house has been freshly painted and new carpet has been installed.  On the main level you’ll find three bedrooms and one additional bathroom. The main area shines with a cozy living room, a dining area which is located next to a lovely kitchen, making it easy to serve meals and ready to host memorable gatherings. The kitchen features Stainless Steel appliances, and off course, granite countertops.   Expand your entertainment possibilities further with the large deck off the kitchen for your indoor-outdoor activities and dining pleasure. Additionally, this lot provides ample space for outdoor games and barbecues, making it an ideal haven for family entertainment and creating lasting memories.   Act now and seize the opportunity to embrace a lifestyle that blends convenience, tranquility, and unparalleled value. Don't let this amazing opportunity pass you by! With an excellent layout, prime location, and overall value, this home is a fantastic find. Schedule a private showing and embark  on your journey to home ownership.   Close to metros: Landover/Cheverly stations/New Carrolton, minutes to DC, not far from  the fabulous Woodmore Town Center Development area, Route 50 and Interstate 495! Located in a prime location for an easy commute to DC, as well as other parts of Maryland and Virginia. Enjoy the convenience of an effortless commute, while relishing in the tranquility of suburban living.
